## Review Loop (Peer Agent Reviews)

All changes go through the **review loop** before shipping:

```
Planner → Implementer → [Review Loop] → Ship
                           ↓
                  Arch Reviewer    → checks layer violations
                  Security Reviewer → checks secrets & auth
                  Reviewer          → final quality gate
                           ↑
              If ANY FAIL → back to Implementer
              If ALL PASS → Ship
```

Each reviewer produces a PASS/FAIL report. The Implementer iterates until all pass.

