## CI Feedback Loop

When CI runs on a PR, the following checks execute automatically:

1. `harnesskit enforce` — validates architecture layer rules
2. `harnesskit doctor` — checks scaffold health & completeness
3. Standard build / test / lint pipeline

If any check fails, the agent reads the CI output and self-corrects:
```
CI Fail → Agent reads logs → Fixes code → Pushes update → CI re-runs
```
This loop repeats until CI is green or the agent requests human help.

